                Send group emails and organize your social life.
                Try out the Demo Login!
                <br />
                <br />
                <strong>Built with pride using cutting edge tech:</strong>
                <br />
                <div class="d-flex align-items-center mt-3">
                    @* Show Techs here*@
                    <figure>
                        <img src="https://devicons.railway.app/i/dot-net.svg" class="imgicon" />
